p.k: In order to live, you need to eat and, in the sea, we imagine that this boils down to one fish eating another. Reality is a bit more complex. réalité est un peu plus complexe. Exacly like on earth, there is a food chain going from the smallest to the biggest... well normally. Each link of the chain is vital for the whole system and is made of specific behaviors often strange and fascinating. The marine world is a never ending source of amazament and will for long... feed our imagination.
